title: War of the Roses: Do YOU have a corkscrew?
description: Lisa is suspicious of her husband Tony because she went on a trip to see family and he texted her something weird about a corkscrew.  Then she saw a photo he had of their dog on a bed that wasn't theirs.  Was Tony getting into trouble while Lisa was out of town?
